Everything Life Has To Offer Oracle

This is a bot. It's supposed to help promote Shari Kasman's book, Everything Life Has To Offer (http://invisiblepublishing.com/product/everything-life-has-to-offer/)

It does a few things:
*Tweets excerpts/missives/'fortunes' at followers
*Tweets news about the book
*Retweets/favourites stuff tweeted by the author, publisher, et al... when appropriate

NOTE: While this application is FREE (GPLv3) the text/sentences/excerpts that it tweets are mostly the property of the author, Shari Kasman, and are being republished with her express permission as well as that of her publisher, Invisible Publishing (http://invisiblepublishing.com/)
